originalText.text: Kumi is truly gifted as she is able to visualize and interpret her aura readings.  I was intrigued by her visions and amazed at how she was able to convey and translate it to what was happening with me.  It's like a light bulb went off and she helped me see things more clearly.  With her help, she gave me an objective view on my life.  Looking forward to our next session as she helps me to see more clearly.

originalText.text: My aura reading with my beloved Kumi was absolutely incredible! The messages that came through my aura were so detailed.  It was as if she were seeing a beautiful depiction of my energy through another time and space and was able to interpret it at level I could understand and benefit from. Kumi’s energy is so gentle and she was so patient with all of my questions. I am looking forward to booking with her again very soon. A must try if you are in NYC!

originalText.text: I could fill pages and pages with good things about Kumi.  I first came to know her from an Aura reading she did a couple of years ago, which was deadly accurate.  But she is so much more than that. I count on her for her wisdom, honesty and the goodness of her gift.  Do yourself a favor and book time with her.  Your soul will thank you.

originalText.text: The reading I had from Kumi was very accurate - she was able to tell a lot about me without being given any information. It was also very interesting to hear about my past life!  Highly recommend!

originalText.text: I had my first aura reading with Kumi a few years back. She told me she saw a stream with a waterfall at the end. Means I was on the right path but I didn't know what was at the end of the path which was accurate because I was still on a goal searching journey. Years later, when Covid happened, she gave me another reading and said that she sees a vast land in a foreign country and I am there in a farm but I live in a big city, and I am just there for a visit, but the land belongs to my family. At that time, I was in LA, I do not own any land. So, I took it as a metaphor. However my husband's family in Sicily are land owners. Soon after Covid hit hard in the US, my husband and I decided to go to Sicily to stay with my mother in law. Her reading came true. I was in a field picking peppers, lettuces, tomatoes.  I never thought an aura reading is a prediction of the future. Perhaps, my aura told Kumi my future and she translated it and related the message to me. The thought of Sicily never came to my mind, but the circumstances had directed me to that direction. I find Kumi is very gifted in her intuition and I highly recommend her if you are at a cross road of life like I was.
